lead_paragraph: Maddie Manning had 16 points and nine rebounds and No. 13 Oklahoma used a strong third quarter to defeat Colorado State 70-55 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Third Quarter Propels No. 13 Oklahoma Women to 70-55 Win
